ComicInfo.Summary:
Summer Spectacular Part Two: Summer recalls food-war stories, while applying for a job in a fast food restaurant.
What Lies in the Clackspire Labyrinth?!: When Beth learns that Jerry turned Rick over to the Time Police, he is banished to the basement, which he dubs "Jerryworld" where "Jerry gets to make the rules!" In moving his mini-fridge to his basement abode, Jerry knocks over a cannister of fluid which releases a large crawling insect-like creature into the house. Rick and Morty are sentenced to life in the Clackspire Labyrinth, where they search for a way out of a maze of horrors... originally designed by Rick!
